Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:20.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《比利小子》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously on Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我被命令在地方法院出庭\N{\rYUANWEN}I've been ordered to appear before the district court
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,面对墨菲和他的同伙捏造的\N{\rYUANWEN}to face those charges of false accounting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:26.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伪造账目和贪污公款的指控\N{\rYUANWEN}and embezzling state funds that Murphy and his pals cooked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认识的一个警官\N{\rYUANWEN}One of the sheriff's deputies I got friendly with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉我麦克斯文\N{\rYUANWEN}told me that McSween's gonna be served with a warrant
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:32.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,会因谋杀从犯而被逮捕\N{\rYUANWEN}for accessory to murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:33.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么 他连法庭都上不了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What, so he doesn't even make it to the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 他告诉我朋友 一旦麦克斯文进了监狱\N{\rYUANWEN}No. He told my friend that once McSween is behind bars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:37.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他就会被判有罪 处以绞刑\N{\rYUANWEN}he'll be found guilty and hanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:40.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布雷迪警长马上就来 一旦我们在法院门前\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Brady will be along shortly and once we've arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,逮捕了麦克斯文\N{\rYUANWEN}McSween in front of the courthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:44.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们所有的麻烦就都解决了\N{\rYUANWEN}all of our troubles will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那不可能 我会阻止布雷迪的\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that's not happenin". I'm gonna stop Brady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:48.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我这就骑马去林肯 谁跟我去\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm ridin'into Lincoln. Who's comin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:53.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们的布雷迪警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Our very own Sheriff Brady gunned down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:57.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被一群歹徒和杀人犯枪杀了\N{\rYUANWEN}by a criminal gang of outlaws and murderers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:03.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们的头目是一个叫比利小子的人\N{\rYUANWEN}all lead by one man who goes by the name of Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:06.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道如果不绞死\N{\rYUANWEN}I know that no one will ever be satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:08.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}until Billy the Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,必然无法平息大家的怒火\N{\rYUANWEN}swings on the end of a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:15.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,戴·托博斯克小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Seiiorita Del Tobosco,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:16.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只想自我介绍一下\N{\rYUANWEN}I just wanted to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:21.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我想要公道 我就必须掌控法律\N{\rYUANWEN}If I want justice, I have to take the law into my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不明白 你跟我说你已经变了\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I can't understand, you told me you changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rYUANWEN}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:27.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你走吧 马上\N{\rYUANWEN}Please go. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:31.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布雷迪警长光天化日之下在大街上\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Brady's murder on Main Street in broad daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:34.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被人谋杀是一起骇人听闻的罪行\N{\rYUANWEN}is an appalling and horrifying crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 瓦尔茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I can assure you, Mr. Walz,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不用多久你就会听到\N{\rYUANWEN}it won't be long before you're hearin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:39.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利小子的死讯\N{\rYUANWEN}of Billy the Kid's demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:42.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦先生刚刚任命了林肯县的新警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Catron has just appointed a new sheriff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:45.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这位警长发誓\N{\rYUANWEN}in Lincoln County. A sheriff who's pledged to drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要把每一个持枪歹徒和不法之徒都赶出这片土地\N{\rYUANWEN}each and every gunman and outlaw out of this territory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:51.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恢复法律和秩序\N{\rYUANWEN}and restore Iaw and order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我建议你和他合作\N{\rYUANWEN}I suggest you co- operate with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:57.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我叫加勒特 帕特·加勒特\N{\rYUANWEN}My name's Garrett, Pat Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西·埃文斯对我们来说是个真正的威胁\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse Evans is a real danger to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们想干什么就干什么 小伙子们\N{\rYUANWEN}We do what we want, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们就特么是法律\N{\rYUANWEN}We are the fuckin'law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:07.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小子在哪 我想听见他求饶\N{\rYUANWEN}Where is The Kid? I want to hear him bleat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:09.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\rYUANWEN}Where is he? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还有机会 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}You still have a chance, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:17.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抓住咯\N{\rYUANWEN}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:18.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,驾 驾\N{\rYUANWEN}He- yah, he- yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:20.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利小子明明就在你眼前\N{\rYUANWEN}You had Billy The Kid in your sights,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你就那么放他走了\N{\rYUANWEN}and you let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他跟个鬼魂一样消失了\N{\rYUANWEN}He vanished like a fuckin'ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会杀了他\N{\rYUANWEN}Pll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我亲自动手\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:30.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这才对嘛\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:35.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们去追杀比利 如此而已 我们要做的就是这事\N{\rYUANWEN}We go after Billy. That's all. That's what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:02.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,巴克绍特 能看到你可太好了 你去哪了\N{\rYUANWEN}Buckshot. Nice of you to show up. Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们给我讲了发生的事\N{\rYUANWEN}They told me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小子就在你面前 可你没开枪\N{\rYUANWEN}You had The Kid in front of you. You didn't throw lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想象不到\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小子像阿帕切人一样朝我冲过来\N{\rYUANWEN}The Kid came up on me just like an Apache.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不知道从哪钻出来的\N{\rYUANWEN}Came outta nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:14.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们来这就是干这个的\N{\rYUANWEN}It's what we're here to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杀了那个小子\N{\rYUANWEN}kill the fuckin'Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你做不到 你知道我可以\N{\rYUANWEN}If you ain't gonna do it, you know I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道他在哪\N{\rYUANWEN}I know where he at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\rYUANWEN}How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就是我的事了\N{\rYUANWEN}That's my business now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不如回去睡觉吧 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Why don't you go back to sleep, Jesse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:38.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要去领赏了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm goin'to collect my reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真好吃啊 布鲁尔\N{\rYUANWEN}Mmm, those are tasty, Brewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:58.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的荣幸 科先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that's my pleasure, Mr. Coe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-谢了 比利 -谢了 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Thanks, Billy. - Thanks, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有人来了\N{\rYUANWEN}Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有人来了\N{\rYUANWEN}Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是巴克绍特吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that Buckshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他来这干什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:27.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许他和杰西闹翻了\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe he had a fallin' out with Jesse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想加入我们\N{\rYUANWEN}Wants to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们待这\N{\rYUANWEN}You guys stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可能比你们所有人都更了解巴克绍特\N{\rYUANWEN}I guess I know Buckshot better than any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我去看看他想干啥\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll just go find out what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,乔治 小心点 那混蛋枪法很准\N{\rYUANWEN}George, be careful, the bastard's a good shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah. I'm aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,扳机指上\N{\rYUANWEN}Finger on the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:09.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好啊 巴克绍特\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey there, Buckshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:12.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}How's things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我来这可是有原因的 乔治\N{\rYUANWEN}I got a good reason to be here, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么原因\N{\rYUANWEN}What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:21.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不能说\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, we ain't telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我们在这的\N{\rYUANWEN}How'd you find out we were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认识一个老印第安侦察兵\N{\rYUANWEN}I know an old Indian scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:32.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟你一样 他找到的你们\N{\rYUANWEN}Same as you. He found ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:35.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,巴克绍特\N{\rYUANWEN}Buckshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你来这肯定有充分的理由\N{\rYUANWEN}There's gotta be a good reason why you came out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Sure there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我来是抓小子的\N{\rYUANWEN}I come to capture The Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,死活不论\N{\rYUANWEN}alive or dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要去领赏\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm gonna claim that reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没疯吧 巴克\N{\rYUANWEN}Have you gone crazy, Buck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不只是比利\N{\rYUANWEN}It's not just Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:02.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,里面还有好几个监管者\N{\rYUANWEN}There's several more Regulators in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:04.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没机会的\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要领赏钱\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm gonna claim that reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:10.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,乔治 动一下啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on, Georgie, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:13.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你看哈 你还因为杀死汤斯顿而被通缉\N{\rYUANWEN}You know what? You're still wanted for killing Tunstall,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:17.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以也许你该向我们投降\N{\rYUANWEN}so maybe you should surrender to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为现在我们是林肯的新法律了\N{\rYUANWEN}since we're the new law here in Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放下枪\N{\rYUANWEN}Put that rifle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,举手投降\N{\rYUANWEN}Throw up your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不怎么样啊 玛丽·安\N{\rYUANWEN}Not much, Mary Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,查理\N{\rYUANWEN}Charlie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你特么个怂包\N{\rYUANWEN}You fuckin coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你在哪呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Where you at? !
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,草\N{\rYUANWEN}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要怎么办啊\N{\rYUANWEN}What the hell are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们都待这别动\N{\rYUANWEN}Y'all stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:04.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他要找的是我\N{\rYUANWEN}It's me he's after.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:10.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,草\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,晚安咯 亲\N{\rYUANWEN}Night, night, darlin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:17.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,草\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得想点办法\N{\rYUANWEN}We gotta do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:25.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,巴克绍特 别开枪\N{\rYUANWEN}Buckshot, hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:27.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我这就出来\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm comin'out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可以活捉我\N{\rYUANWEN}You can take me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快 快 快\N{\rYUANWEN}Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我把枪放下了\N{\rYUANWEN}Puttin'my rifle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就我和你\N{\rYUANWEN}It's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:04.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别动 放下\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't. Leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,草泥马 草\N{\rYUANWEN}Fuck you. Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:13.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你要找我\N{\rYUANWEN}You lookin for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:14.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你找我哈\N{\rYUANWEN}You looking for me, huh? -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:15.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\rYUANWEN}Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,米德尔顿和布鲁尔都死了\N{\rYUANWEN}Middleton and Brewer are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:09.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我敢说查理不会有事 他非常幸运\N{\rYUANWEN}I can report that Charlie will live. He's been very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:14.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:24.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麦克斯文先生让我给你带个话 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. McSween asked me to pass on some news to you, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看起来他们又派了新警长\N{\rYUANWEN}It seems they've appointed a new sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,叫帕特·加勒特\N{\rYUANWEN}Name's Pat Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帕特·加勒特\N{\rYUANWEN}Pat Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:32.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是这么说的 这名字你熟悉吗\N{\rYUANWEN}That's what he said. Does that name mean something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rYUANWEN}It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要跟他聊聊\N{\rYUANWEN}I need to speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得你不该进林肯县 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't think you should ride into Lincoln, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,县里到处都是通缉你的海报\N{\rYUANWEN}There's Wanted posters up all over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可能会被当场射杀\N{\rYUANWEN}You could be shot on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我就给他写封信\N{\rYUANWEN}Then I'll write to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,亲爱的帕特 许久不见\N{\rYUANWEN}Dear Pat, been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恭喜你被任命为林肯县警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Congratulations on being made sheriff of Lincoln County.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我一直都知道你早晚会有所成就\N{\rYUANWEN}I always knew you'd make something of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你走后这里就变了\N{\rYUANWEN}Look, things have changed since you left and they're gonna try
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们肯定想让你听他们的\N{\rYUANWEN}and bend your ear to their will,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但千万别听浩世\N{\rYUANWEN}but don't listen to the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:28.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别听墨菲或者莱利的\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't listen to Murphy or Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲是圣达菲环的一员\N{\rYUANWEN}Murphy belongs to the Santa Fe ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而莱利只是个杀手\N{\rYUANWEN}and Riley's just a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们都是骗子\N{\rYUANWEN}They're both crooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯县就是个屎坑\N{\rYUANWEN}Lincoln is a cesspit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,需要清理\N{\rYUANWEN}and what it needs is cleanin'up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你就是那个人\N{\rYUANWEN}and you're the man to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你需要监管者的帮助\N{\rYUANWEN}with the help of the Regulators.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:47.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你永远的朋友 威廉·H·邦尼\N{\rYUANWEN}Always your friend, William H. Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早 警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Mornin', Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他叫巴克绍特·罗伯特\N{\rYUANWEN}His name is Buckshot Roberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西·埃文斯帮派的新成员\N{\rYUANWEN}Recent member of Jesse Evans' gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他这是怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:25.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他说他可以独自追捕比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}He said that he could hunt down Billy the Kid on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他跟浩世的莱利先生也是这么说的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's what he told Mr. Riley up at the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:31.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说他会像捕杀野兽一样杀了比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}That he'd hunt The Kid down like an animal and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看上去似乎正相反\N{\rYUANWEN}Looks like, maybe, it was the other way round.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他告诉别人小子的藏身之处了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Did he tell anyone he'd found The Kid's hideaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得没有\N{\rYUANWEN}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我们就继续找吧\N{\rYUANWEN}We'll just have to keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:51.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉杰西·埃文斯我想马上见他\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell Jesse Evans I want to see him right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有\N{\rYUANWEN}And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找到罗伯特先生的家人\N{\rYUANWEN}find Mr. Roberts' family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他需要体面的安葬\N{\rYUANWEN}He needs a decent burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rYUANWEN}Yah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,散了吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:00.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,沃尔兹先生 欢迎\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Walz. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,戴·托博斯克爵士\N{\rYUANWEN}Sir Del Tobosco,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我给你介绍一下 这位是卡特伦先生\N{\rYUANWEN}may I introduce you to Mr. Catron?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我当然知道你是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很荣幸\N{\rYUANWEN}It is a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我给你介绍一下 这是我妻子伊莎贝拉\N{\rYUANWEN}May I present to you my wife, Isabella?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们不如进去吧 外面太他妈冷了\N{\rYUANWEN}How about we go inside? It's damn cold out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 请\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要来点香槟吗 卡特伦先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Can I offer you some champagne, Mr. Catron?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢 我喝威士忌\N{\rYUANWEN}No, thank you. I'll take a whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请上威士忌\N{\rYUANWEN}Whiskey, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你家人吗\N{\rYUANWEN}This your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes. Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我猜他们都死了 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm guessin'they're all dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\rYUANWEN}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:59.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找我有什么事吗 卡特伦先生 请坐\N{\rYUANWEN}...how can I help you, Mr. Catron? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你开玩笑呢是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you kiddin' me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦银行和信托公司是我的\N{\rYUANWEN}I own Catron Bank and Trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:11.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我知道 -也许你不知道\N{\rYUANWEN}- Yes, I know. - Well, maybe you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:14.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是沃尔兹先生会告诉你的 对吧 沃尔兹先生\N{\rYUANWEN}But Mr. Walz is about to tell you. Isn't that right, Mr. Walz?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:15.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事实上 戴·托博斯克先生\N{\rYUANWEN}The fact is, Mr. Del Tobosco,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:21.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在过去两年中\N{\rYUANWEN}that over the last two years you have applied for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:24.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你向卡特伦银行和信托公司\N{\rYUANWEN}and been given many substantial loans
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:25.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,申请并获得了许多大笔贷款\N{\rYUANWEN}from the Catron Bank and Trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因此\N{\rYUANWEN}As a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:32.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在你负债超过10万美元\N{\rYUANWEN}you are in debt now over $100, 000.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,托博斯克先生 我一般不会\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't normally call personally on those in debt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,亲自拜访欠银行债的人\N{\rYUANWEN}to the bank, Mr. Tobosco,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:39.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我为你破例了\N{\rYUANWEN}but for you I have made an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:42.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你看哈 用你的财产和其他利益进行担保\N{\rYUANWEN}You see, $100, 000 is a large amount of money
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,借款10万美元 这是个不小的数字\N{\rYUANWEN}secured by your property and other interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:49.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我很好奇你打算如何以及何时偿还债务\N{\rYUANWEN}so I'm curious how and when you intend to repay your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你其实完全没必要这么大老远\N{\rYUANWEN}You had no need to travel this far to ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跑来问我这个问题 卡特伦先生\N{\rYUANWEN}this question, Mr. Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:58.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可以向你保证一千次\N{\rYUANWEN}I could have reassured you a thousand times
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:00.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为事实上 我正在兑现几项投资\N{\rYUANWEN}for the fact is that I am in the process of cashing in
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并出售在西班牙的房产\N{\rYUANWEN}several investments and selling property in Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是嘛\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是拿我当傻子了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you take me for a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,意思就是你在撒谎\N{\rYUANWEN}I mean you're lyin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:29.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不信什么家族财富之类的鬼话\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't buy all this family wealth shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,根本没有所谓家族财富\N{\rYUANWEN}There is no family wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就算曾经有过 也早没了\N{\rYUANWEN}And if once there was, it's long gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能早被这房间里挂着的死人们\N{\rYUANWEN}probably spent by and squandered
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都花光了\N{\rYUANWEN}by all these dead guys around the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你以为我会信西班牙黄金吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You think I believe in Spanish gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 当然不会\N{\rYUANWEN}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:47.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你那古老的头衔和优越感\N{\rYUANWEN}Your ancient titles and your sense of entitlement
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:48.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一点也打动不了我\N{\rYUANWEN}don't impress me one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:50.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是美国人\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm an American.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们不吃那套\N{\rYUANWEN}We don't do that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们只务实\N{\rYUANWEN}We deal in what's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:59.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而你不实 对我来说不是\N{\rYUANWEN}And you're not real, not to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:02.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 戴·托博斯克先生\N{\rYUANWEN}So, Mr. Del Tobosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:07.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你要付的账单\N{\rYUANWEN}Here's your bill to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:10.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你的总借款\N{\rYUANWEN}It's your, um, total borrowings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:13.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加上累积利息 再加上费用\N{\rYUANWEN}plus, of course, accumulated interest, plus fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:14.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而这个\N{\rYUANWEN}And here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 一封信\N{\rYUANWEN}is a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是一封你写给银行的信\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a letter from you to the bank
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:24.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,同意在28天内\N{\rYUANWEN}agreeing to repay all monies owed in full
