Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.57,0:25:33.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是比利 找达尔西尼亚\N{\rYUANWEN}It's Billy, for Dulcinea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.18,0:25:52.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rYUANWEN}Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.18,0:25:54.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,屋顶上\N{\rYUANWEN}Up on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.76,0:25:55.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rYUANWEN}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.77,0:25:57.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\rYUANWEN}Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.10,0:25:58.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rYUANWEN}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:11.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们把守卫杀了\N{\rYUANWEN}They killed the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.07,0:26:13.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办\N{\rYUANWEN}What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.45,0:26:15.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,祈祷 儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}Pray, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.66,0:26:17.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们祈祷\N{\rYUANWEN}Let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.37,0:26:20.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,圣母玛利亚 天主之母\N{\rYUANWEN}Holy Mary, Mother of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.79,0:26:22.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,求你为我们这些罪人祈求\N{\rYUANWEN}pray for us sinners,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.54,0:26:24.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在和我们临终的时刻 阿门\N{\rYUANWEN}now and at the hour of our death. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.71,0:26:28.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.01,0:26:35.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我去跟他们谈\N{\rYUANWEN}I will go speak with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.60,0:26:36.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要 求你 亲爱的\N{\rYUANWEN}No! No! Please, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.31,0:26:40.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,爸爸 他们都是杀人犯和强盗\N{\rYUANWEN}Papa, they are killers and thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.85,0:26:41.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我们得去跟他们谈 亲爱的 -不要 爸爸 别去\N{\rYUANWEN}We've got to talk to them, sweetheart.\NNo Papa! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.81,0:26:42.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一 戎们得去氓他们谈羊笈的一个晏仓仓别去\N-我们得去跟他们谈 亲爱的 -不要 爸爸 别去\N{\rYUANWEN}We've got to talk to them, sweetheart.\NPapa, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.06,0:26:45.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让我做我该做的 亲爱的 拜托\N{\rYUANWEN}Let me do what I have to do, my darling. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.98,0:26:49.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道那些人想要什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I know what those men want.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.37,0:26:56.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我去拿武器\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm going to get my weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.03,0:27:30.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.03,0:27:39.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别开枪 等等\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't shoot! Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.29,0:27:40.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,停火\N{\rYUANWEN}Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.46,0:27:46.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们是卡特伦先生派来的\N{\rYUANWEN}We've been sent by Mr. Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.84,0:27:49.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不是来乞求你\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not here to beg you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.05,0:27:51.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或者恳求你的\N{\rYUANWEN}or to plead with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.21,0:27:52.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而是要求你们\N{\rYUANWEN}but to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.84,0:27:55.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要进我的房子\N{\rYUANWEN}do not come in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.59,0:27:57.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我家人在里面\N{\rYUANWEN}My family are inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.80,0:28:01.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果卡特伦先生想要我的东西 所有东西\N{\rYUANWEN}And if Mr. Catron wants my belongings, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.27,0:28:04.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的马 我的牛 他都可以拿走\N{\rYUANWEN}my horses, my cattle, he can have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.14,0:28:05.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会把一切都转让给他\N{\rYUANWEN}I will sign it all over to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:07.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你去把这话告诉他\N{\rYUANWEN}You go and tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.56,0:28:10.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但不可以跨过我的门槛\N{\rYUANWEN}But don't cross my threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.57,0:28:13.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没有这个权利\N{\rYUANWEN}You have no right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.82,0:28:15.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们怎么都还是要进去的\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, we're going to do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.78,0:28:19.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我屋里有持枪人员\N{\rYUANWEN}I have armed men inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.08,0:28:21.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们阻止不了我们的\N{\rYUANWEN}They're not gonna stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.16,0:28:25.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别挡道 老头\N{\rYUANWEN}Get outta the way, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.21,0:28:29.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rYUANWEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.46,0:28:33.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我说了别挡道\N{\rYUANWEN}I said get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.09,0:28:35.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们是魔鬼\N{\rYUANWEN}You're devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.97,0:28:38.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们是魔鬼 你们都是\N{\rYUANWEN}- You're devils, all of you! -
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.14,0:28:40.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 爸爸\N{\rYUANWEN}No, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.22,0:29:23.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这边 兄弟们\N{\rYUANWEN}Over here, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.99,0:29:38.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们检查过那个房间了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you check that room yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.28,0:29:41.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这里面人都搞定了 你们找到什么了\N{\rYUANWEN}Everyone done in here! What do ya got?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.55,0:30:43.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.55,0:30:46.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你的\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not gonna hurt ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.27,0:30:58.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是达尔西尼亚 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You're Dulcinea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.24,0:31:01.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是比利的女人\N{\rYUANWEN}You're Billy's girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.74,0:31:04.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害比利女朋友的\N{\rYUANWEN}I wouldn't hurt Billy's girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.24,0:31:05.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利和我\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.58,0:31:09.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很久以前 就是朋友了\N{\rYUANWEN}we're friends from...from way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.41,0:31:13.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他就像是我自家兄弟\N{\rYUANWEN}He's like my own brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.54,0:31:14.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不许动\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.59,0:31:18.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把枪放下 达尔西尼亚\N{\rYUANWEN}Put the gun down, Dulcinea.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.01,0:31:22.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托 听我说\N{\rYUANWEN}Please. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.13,0:31:26.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你的 拜托\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not going to hurt you. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.41,0:31:47.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我 天使\N{\rYUANWEN}It's me, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.03,0:31:49.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我 别出声\N{\rYUANWEN}It's me, don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.46,0:31:56.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小姐 你得赶紧走\N{\rYUANWEN}Sehorita, you have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.29,0:31:59.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那帮混蛋很快就会来找你\N{\rYUANWEN}Those bastards will come for you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.38,0:32:02.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.67,0:32:04.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你先走 我随后就到\N{\rYUANWEN}Go on ahead, I will catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.34,0:32:06.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先保护自己\N{\rYUANWEN}Save yourself, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.43,0:32:09.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rYUANWEN}Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.35,0:32:55.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,达尔西尼亚 你没事吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Dulcinea! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.89,0:33:34.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢啊 朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}Thanks, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.22,0:33:36.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我的荣幸 比利一如既往\N{\rYUANWEN}It's an honor, Billy. As always.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.29,0:33:55.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rYUANWEN}Hola.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.21,0:33:58.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗨 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Hi, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.43,0:34:15.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道枪手是谁 但\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know who the gunmen were, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.93,0:34:18.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道这事跟圣达菲一个\N{\rYUANWEN}I know it was connected to a recent visit
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.81,0:34:21.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,银行老板近期来访有关\N{\rYUANWEN}by a man who owns a bank in Santa Fe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.44,0:34:25.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,托马斯·卡特伦\N{\rYUANWEN}Thomas Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.94,0:34:28.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他威胁要让我父亲破产\N{\rYUANWEN}He threatened to make my father bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.90,0:34:31.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们都知道卡特伦是个什么样的人\N{\rYUANWEN}We know all about Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.30,0:34:47.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.90,0:35:07.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们把所有人都杀了 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}They killed everyone, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.19,0:35:11.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我全\N{\rYUANWEN}My whole...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.70,0:35:14.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我全家 -我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}- My whole family. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.29,0:35:18.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你现在安全了 好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}But you're safe, though, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.20,0:35:21.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟我一起\N{\rYUANWEN}With me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.67,0:35:24.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会保护你的 我保证\N{\rYUANWEN}I'|| protect you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.59,0:35:28.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会为你家人报仇\N{\rYUANWEN}And I will avenge your family's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.50,0:35:30.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我发誓\N{\rYUANWEN}I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.22,0:35:35.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,其中一个枪手假装是你 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}One of the gunmen pretended to be you, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.72,0:35:39.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们就是这么进到庄园里来的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's how they got into the compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.85,0:35:44.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他说你们像亲兄弟一样\N{\rYUANWEN}He said you were like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.10,0:35:47.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我 我不知道他是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}I- I don't know who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.74,0:35:54.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.51,0:36:11.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早啊 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Mornin°, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.26,0:36:14.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.51,0:36:15.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.55,0:36:18.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,往那边看\N{\rYUANWEN}Look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.77,0:36:22.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.06,0:36:25.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加勒特警长 很高兴见到你\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Garrett, it's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.56,0:36:26.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲在吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is Murphy around?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.81,0:36:28.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.95,0:36:35.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲少校\N{\rYUANWEN}Major Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.95,0:36:39.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帕特·加勒特警长决定来拜访我们\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Pat Garrett has decided to pay us a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.49,0:36:42.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请进 警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on in, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.79,0:36:46.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.67,0:36:53.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别来无恙\N{\rYUANWEN}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.13,0:36:57.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还成吧 没什么可抱怨的\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right. Can't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.97,0:36:59.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,发现很难从这把椅子上站起来\N{\rYUANWEN}Find it hard to get up out of this chair
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.68,0:37:01.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟你正式问个好 所以\N{\rYUANWEN}to properly greet ya, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.06,0:37:04.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就原谅我站不起来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}forgive me if I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.77,0:37:06.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.44,0:37:09.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你喝威士忌吗 加勒特警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you drink whiskey, Sheriff Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.61,0:37:12.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早上不喝\N{\rYUANWEN}Not in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.61,0:37:15.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,随便你\N{\rYUANWEN}Aye. Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.62,0:37:23.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.55,0:37:36.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还记得我们第一次见面吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you remember the first time we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.01,0:37:38.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然记得\N{\rYUANWEN}Sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.97,0:37:40.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布雷迪警长刚抓了我\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Brady had just arrested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.85,0:37:41.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.76,0:37:44.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就是那个\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I was the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.64,0:37:46.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说服他放你一马的人\N{\rYUANWEN}who persuaded him to get you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.48,0:37:50.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把你训练成一个执法者\N{\rYUANWEN}Train you up as a lawman.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.02,0:37:53.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你真是太好了 我很感激\N{\rYUANWEN}That was very good of you. I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.70,0:38:01.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是在非常困难的时期来的 非常困难\N{\rYUANWEN}You've come at a very difficult time, very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.82,0:38:03.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,外面正在打一场全面的战争\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a full- scale war going on out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.53,0:38:04.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rYUANWEN}So, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.50,0:38:08.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们在这里为美国的价值观而战\N{\rYUANWEN}We're fighting for American values here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.16,0:38:09.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道的对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.00,0:38:14.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,美国人的价值观对上北方投机佬\N{\rYUANWEN}American values against carpetbaggers,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.88,0:38:18.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,外地人 罪犯 杀人犯\N{\rYUANWEN}out- of- staters, criminals, murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.18,0:38:22.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这也是卡特伦先生让我相信的\N{\rYUANWEN}That is what Mr. Catron led me to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.68,0:38:25.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道你以前跟比利一道的\N{\rYUANWEN}I know you used to ride with Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.64,0:38:28.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rYUANWEN}And now it's.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.48,0:38:30.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的任务是追捕他们\N{\rYUANWEN}Now it's your job to hunt them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.52,0:38:31.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你对此有什么想法\N{\rYUANWEN}How do you feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.98,0:38:35.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的工作是在林肯县执法\N{\rYUANWEN}It's my job to administer the law in Lincoln County.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.23,0:38:39.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你在这方面能协助我 墨菲先生\N{\rYUANWEN}And I hope that you will assist me in that endeavor, Mr. Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.20,0:38:40.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.24,0:38:43.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,取决于你站在法律哪一边了\N{\rYUANWEN}Dependin'on what side of the Iaw you're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.20,0:38:46.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,法律不偏袒任何一方\N{\rYUANWEN}The law doesn't take sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.54,0:38:47.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不会吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.50,0:38:53.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那小子就在大街上杀了你的上一任\N{\rYUANWEN}The Kid killed your predecessor right out there on Main Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.04,0:38:56.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,冷血的将他击杀\N{\rYUANWEN}Shot him down in cold blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.63,0:38:58.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这件事你站哪边\N{\rYUANWEN}Whose side are you on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.47,0:39:01.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我站正义的一边\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm on the side of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.47,0:39:04.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.10,0:39:07.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们也没什么不同\N{\rYUANWEN}we're not so different,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.43,0:39:09.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对吧 加勒特先生 完全没有不同\N{\rYUANWEN}are we, Mr. Garrett? Not so different at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.98,0:39:11.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\rYUANWEN}You and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.89,0:39:13.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们是伙伴\N{\rYUANWEN}we're partners here,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.52,0:39:17.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为在林肯 我们想要的只有正义\N{\rYUANWEN}because that's all we want here in Lincoln, justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.73,0:39:19.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们只想要这个\N{\rYUANWEN}That's all we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.99,0:39:22.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而我想要的 加勒特警长\N{\rYUANWEN}And all I want, Sheriff Garrett...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.87,0:39:28.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只想看到\N{\rYUANWEN}...is nothing more
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.20,0:39:31.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他妈的比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}than to see that Billy the fucking Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.58,0:39:32.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被挂在绞刑架上\N{\rYUANWEN}hanging on the end of a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.59,0:39:37.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你明白我意思吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.09,0:39:45.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.15,0:39:59.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么大家都聚在这里 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Why are all these men here, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.98,0:40:00.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么大家都聚在这里 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Why are all these men here, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.99,0:40:04.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为我们要接管这个镇\N{\rYUANWEN}Because we're going to take over the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.70,0:40:11.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你真能做到吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can you really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.04,0:40:14.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在时机到了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.00,0:40:21.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯的人民已经厌倦了\N{\rYUANWEN}The people of Lincoln are tired
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.30,0:40:23.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,无法无天和混乱不堪\N{\rYUANWEN}of the lawlessness and the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.01,0:40:26.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨西哥人也受够了被剥削\N{\rYUANWEN}And the Mexicans are sick of being exploited.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.14,0:40:29.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们想要改变\N{\rYUANWEN}They want change.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.31,0:40:31.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿先生试图给他们带来改变\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Tunstall tried to give it to'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.97,0:40:34.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但 他失败了\N{\rYUANWEN}but. ...he couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.94,0:40:37.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想成功\N{\rYUANWEN}I intend to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.69,0:40:46.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道我们还要再过几天才会转移\N{\rYUANWEN}You know we're not moving out for a few more days yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.86,0:40:49.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 我可以把你转移到个安全的地方\N{\rYUANWEN}So, I could move you somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.08,0:40:52.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,静悄悄的转移\N{\rYUANWEN}Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.83,0:40:55.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.23,0:41:18.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,兄弟\N{\rYUANWEN}Whoa, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.80,0:41:45.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.21,0:41:46.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好 曼努埃拉\N{\rYUANWEN}Hola, Manuela.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.59,0:41:49.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这位是达尔西尼亚·戴·托博斯克小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}This is Seiorita Dulcinea Del Tobosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.26,0:41:51.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她需要找个安全的地方躲一阵子\N{\rYUANWEN}She needs somewhere safe to hold up for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.22,0:41:52.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望她能在你这里暂住\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm hopin' she can stay here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.72,0:41:54.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可以 比利 没问题\N{\rYUANWEN}Si, Billy. It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.52,0:41:56.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要愿意的话 你可以把马系那边\N{\rYUANWEN}You can tie your horse over there, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.89,0:41:57.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好 谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.03,0:42:07.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西和他的团伙杀了她全家\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse and his gang killed her whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.49,0:42:15.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来 亲爱的孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Come, my sweet child.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.00,0:42:17.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会照顾你的\N{\rYUANWEN}We will take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.37,0:42:20.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢 曼努埃拉\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, Manuela.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.25,0:42:22.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你人真的好好\N{\rYUANWEN}You are very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.17,0:42:25.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会成为你们的负担的\N{\rYUANWEN}I will not be a burden to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.46,0:42:29.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可以一起为你丈夫祈祷 查理\N{\rYUANWEN}And together we can pray for your husband, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.63,0:42:30.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有比利\N{\rYUANWEN}...and Billy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.34,0:42:32.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有其他人\N{\rYUANWEN}and the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.97,0:42:35.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上帝会慈悲的拯救他们的\N{\rYUANWEN}God, in his mercy, will save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.99,0:42:57.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.70,0:42:58.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为什么对不起\N{\rYUANWEN}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.41,0:43:03.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我之前跟你说我不明白你为什么要开战\N{\rYUANWEN}I told you I didn't understand why you needed to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.88,0:43:07.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要再次成为一个法外之徒 还要冒生命危险\N{\rYUANWEN}To become an outlaw again and to risk your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.17,0:43:11.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我当时不理解 但 我现在懂了\N{\rYUANWEN}I didn't understand, but......now I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.80,0:43:15.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,之前的我太天真了\N{\rYUANWEN}I was so naive,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.81,0:43:17.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但一切都变了\N{\rYUANWEN}but everything has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.85,0:43:20.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很抱歉这事发生在你身上\N{\rYUANWEN}I am so sorry this happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.98,0:43:26.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想你死 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want you to die, Billy. T
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.69,0:43:28.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想我们在一起\N{\rYUANWEN}I want us to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.11,0:43:31.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想我们长长久久的在一起\N{\rYUANWEN}I want us to be together for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.37,0:43:41.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我第一次见到你 就想这样了\N{\rYUANWEN}That is all I've wanted since the first moment I saw you.
